item.description: I am a research assistant at National Tsing Hua University supervised by Prof. Min Sun. After taking CS61A and CS70 at U.C. Berkeley and Machine Learning by Prof. Hsuan-Tien Lin at National Taiwan University, I found my passion in Computer Science and decided to pursue Ph.D./M.S in CS to consolidate my research career.
